\c 108
\s Mwari Mubatsiri wedu ngaarumbidzwe
\d Rwiyo, Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Mwoyo wangu wakasimba, Mwari; Ndichaimba, zvirokwazvo, ndichaimba nziyo dzokurumbidza, nomweya wangu wose.
\v 2 Muka iwe mutengeranwa nembira; Ini ndimene ndichamuka mangwanani.
\v 3 Ndichakuvongai Jehovha, pakati pendudzi dzavanhu; Ndichakuimbirai nziyo dzokurumbidza
\s pakati pavahedheni.
\p
\v 4 Nokuti ngoni dzenyu ihuru kumusoro kwokudenga-denga,
\s Uye zvokwadi yenyu inosvikira kudenga rose.
\p
\v 5 Imi mukudzwe Mwari, kumusoro kwokudenga-denga; Kurumbidzwa kwenyu ngakuve kumusoro kwapasi pose.
\p
\v 6 Kuti vadikanwi venyu varwirwe, Tiponesei noruoko rwenyu rworudyi, mutipindure.
\p
\v 7 Mwari akataura pautsvene hwake, achiti, "Ndichafara kwazvo; Ndichaganhura Shekemu, ndichayera mupata weSukoti.
\p
\v 8 Gireadhi ndeyangu naManase ndeyangu;
\s Efuremuwo inhaviro yomusoro wangu;
\p Judha ndiyo tsvimbo yangu youshe.
\v 9 Moabhu ndiwo mudziyo wangu wokushambidzira;
\s Pamusoro peEdhomu ndipo pandichakandira
\s shangu yangu;
\s Ndichapururudza nokuda kwaFirisitia."
\s IoNdianiko achandiisa muguta rakakombwa namasvingo? Ndianiko achandiperekedza
\s ndiende Edhomu?
\s nHamuna kutirasha here, Mwari? Hamubudi Mwari, nehondo dzedu.
\p
\v 12 Tibatsirei pamudzivisi wedu;
\s Nokuti kubatsira kwavanhu hakuna maturo.
\p
\v 13 MunaMwari tichaita noumhare; Nokuti ndiye achatsika vadzivisi vedu pasi.
\s Efuremuwo inhaviro yomusoro wangu;
\p Judha ndiyo tsvimbo yangu youshe.
\v 9 Moabhu ndiwo mudziyo wangu wokushambidzira;
\s Pamusoro peEdhomu ndipo pandichakandira
\s shangu yangu;
\s Ndichapururudza nokuda kwaFirisitia."
\s IoNdianiko achandiisa muguta rakakombwa namasvingo? Ndianiko achandiperekedza
\s ndiende Edhomu?
\s nHamuna kutirasha here, Mwari? Hamubudi Mwari, nehondo dzedu.
\p
\v 12 Tibatsirei pamudzivisi wedu;
\s Nokuti kubatsira kwavanhu hakuna maturo.
\p
\v 13 MunaMwari tichaita noumhare; Nokuti ndiye achatsika vadzivisi vedu pasi.
\s Efuremuwo inhaviro yomusoro wangu;
\p Judha ndiyo tsvimbo yangu youshe.
\v 9 Moabhu ndiwo mudziyo wangu wokushambidzira;
\s Pamusoro peEdhomu ndipo pandichakandira
\s shangu yangu;
\s Ndichapururudza nokuda kwaFirisitia."
\s IoNdianiko achandiisa muguta rakakombwa namasvingo? Ndianiko achandiperekedza
\s ndiende Edhomu?
\s nHamuna kutirasha here, Mwari? Hamubudi Mwari, nehondo dzedu.
\p
